One of them is a _news server, web/news gateway and IMAP server_ 
with a 32 Gb. SCSI software raid, four ATM LANE's on top of an 155Mb 
FORE PCA-200E -thanks Werner!-, one Fast Ether, etc.; the second 
one is also SCSI, fast-ether and runs an enormous _PKS server_ 
(Horowitz-0.9.4) the third one is the one I am using right now, 
_laptop_ ,IBM Thinkpad, pcmcia, apm, etc.
